    FETCH_ROLE_SUCCESS: "FETCH_ROLE_SUCCESS",
    FETCH_ROLE_FAILED: "FETCH_ROLE_FAILED",

    CREATE_USER_FAILED: "CREATE_USER_FAILED",

    FETCH_ALL_USER_START: "FETCH_ALL_USER_START",
